  (67189190, 38904439, 'Punchlist', NULL, '1. Stake a rebar with the hose bib so it doesn''t break when she attaches a hose to it.  Very flexible right now and will break. (Done)
2. Fill manifold with weed barrier and Del Rio gravel. 
3. Patch stucco area near 2 steps coming down from basketball court (Jorge knows what needs to be done).  They already repaired once and it just cracked and peeled right off.
4. Remove blue tape from step lights WITH RAZOR and clean with alcohol when done. Lights are showing blue at night! 
5.  Missing a lot of plants. See attached plans.
6. Fix loose block cap at slump wall and remove the trashed piece that was left there.(done)
7. Double check leveling on basketball hoop( backboard off level)
8. Once we place plants, we can use 6-8 boulders from front yard to fill holes in backyard and stabilize hillside area. 
9. (1) Lomandra Breeze is buried in the mulch area, please move some mulch towards bottom of fence area to fill in.
10. BROKEN bottom of gutter needs new one. See photo.(done)
11. MULCH was supposed to cover all the area in GREEN, I am unsure how much was ordered, but our scope includes mulching and weed barrier on the small hillside behind basketball court as well as irrigation. We need to consider they will be have plants behind BBQ that we are to irrigate with our new drip system.', '2025-06-09', '2025-06-18 11:42:30', 'Brian Godley', '(.PM) Jorge Flores'),
